CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 24, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "Win Alpha Wives Prizes...These are the bridge prize winners who walked off with handsome orchid corsages last Saturday at Kaufman's [sic] when Alpha Wives gave a charming bridge party. Left to right; Mmes. Clara Sands, Doris Griffith, Jewel Blow, Rosa Simmons and Minnie Davis. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Alpha Wives, from left: Clara Sands, Doris Griffith, Jewel Blow, Rosa Simmons, and Minnie Davis, standing in Kaufmann's dining room with leaf patterned rug and landscape painting
